         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JMR">
            <p> . . . ] a copy was deposited in the Property-archive when Claudius Diogenes Dometinus was stephanephoros for the fourth time. I make it clear also in this inscription that in my will I have left 
            1000 denarii to the gerousia - the sources from which this sum is to be given I have indicated in the will - with a view to their being lent out at interest, and from 
            the resulting interest on it used for a lottery for 120 named persons; and to the winners for the giving of 9 <foreign xml:lang="la">assaria</foreign> at my heroon. </p>
         </div>
